  "difficultyLevel": 5,
  "lyrics": "And it's going down tonight You're gonna see the light Hope you will Oh, I see it all clear It's clear of you One by one it's the end of me and you When we're floating away in our fantasies Making our life free to be What we should be, yeah But instead of the beautiful We look at our devices and vices Are we willing to pay the price for what we think is right? One by one we go One by one, baby, it all goes to the line Through this, through all the lines And generational break is back And the old mind, the old mind knows where we wanna be Forget yourself and your jealousy Forget the pride and everything that kills us inside All of it is just you Like everyone else, me and you As we're walking down our line Just know that we wanna find correct ways to grow Make a moment instead of throwing it away You don't let anyone else take it away I said one by one, baby, it goes down to the line One by one, baby, we all end in time One by one, we're gonna rise past the line One by one, baby, it all goes down inside of our divine mind, yeah Break away from the lie you've been taught and just shine Don't care about judgement, be who you're meant to see One by one we break away One by one we find a way One by one we all came to play Why won't you come play with me again? Why are you running away from the fear inside you? One by one we find our way to the high rise One by one, baby, it goes down to the end And that line passes now",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 13.899999618530273,
      "text": "And it's going down tonight You're gonna see the light",
      "start": 6.880000114440918
    },
    {
      "end": 15.9399995803833,
      "text": "Hope you will",
      "start": 13.899999618530273
    },
    {
      "end": 27.100000381469727,
      "text": "Oh, I see it all clear It's clear of you",
      "start": 19.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 31.84000015258789,
      "text": "One by one it's the end of me and you",
      "start": 27.100000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 37.65999984741211,
      "text": "When we're floating away in our fantasies",
      "start": 31.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 43.36000061035156,
      "text": "Making our life free to be",
      "start": 38.220001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 46.34000015258789,
      "text": "What we should be, yeah",
      "start": 43.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 49.939998626708984,
      "text": "But instead of the beautiful",
      "start": 46.34000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 55.08000183105469,
      "text": "We look at our devices and vices",
      "start": 49.939998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 63.08000183105469,
      "text": "Are we willing to pay the price for what we think is right?",
      "start": 55.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 67.76000213623047,
      "text": "One by one we go",
      "start": 63.70000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 76.16000366210938,
      "text": "One by one, baby, it all goes to the line",
      "start": 68.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 79.94000244140625,
      "text": "Through this, through all the lines",
      "start": 76.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 83.54000091552734,
      "text": "And generational break is back",
      "start": 79.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 91.27999877929688,
      "text": "And the old mind, the old mind knows where we wanna be",
      "start": 83.54000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 94.63999938964844,
      "text": "Forget yourself and your jealousy",
      "start": 91.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 100.22000122070312,
      "text": "Forget the pride and everything that kills us inside",
      "start": 94.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 104.08000183105469,
      "text": "All of it is just you",
      "start": 100.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 108.23999786376953,
      "text": "Like everyone else, me and you",
      "start": 104.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 111.68000030517578,
      "text": "As we're walking down our line",
      "start": 108.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 121.13999938964844,
      "text": "Just know that we wanna find correct ways to grow",
      "start": 112.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 128.13999938964844,
      "text": "Make a moment instead of throwing it away",
      "start": 121.5999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 135.86000061035156,
      "text": "You don't let anyone else take it away",
      "start": 129.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 141.97999572753906,
      "text": "I said one by one, baby, it goes down to the line",
      "start": 135.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 150.60000610351562,
      "text": "One by one, baby, we all end in time",
      "start": 144.02000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 158.4600067138672,
      "text": "One by one, we're gonna rise past the line",
      "start": 151.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 166.4600067138672,
      "text": "One by one, baby, it all goes down inside of our divine mind, yeah",
      "start": 159.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 173.83999633789062,
      "text": "Break away from the lie you've been taught and just shine",
      "start": 167.32000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 181.9600067138672,
      "text": "Don't care about judgement, be who you're meant to see",
      "start": 174.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 185.66000366210938,
      "text": "One by one we break away",
      "start": 182.0399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 189.6199951171875,
      "text": "One by one we find a way",
      "start": 185.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 197.0800018310547,
      "text": "One by one we all came to play",
      "start": 189.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 203.86000061035156,
      "text": "Why won't you come play with me again?",
      "start": 197.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 212.0399932861328,
      "text": "Why are you running away from the fear inside you?",
      "start": 205.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 219.05999755859375,
      "text": "One by one we find our way to the high rise",
      "start": 212.0399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 225.27999877929688,
      "text": "One by one, baby, it goes down to the end",
      "start": 219.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 227.97999572753906,
      "text": "And that line passes now",
      "start": 225.27999877929688
    }
  ],
